en dinner for two. The give aways start in just a few days. For details on what my team has put up for you, <a href=\"https://www.thelocaltribe.com/go-win-free-movie-tickets-and-dinner-in-delhi-ncr/\">check it out here</a> . Tell your friends too about it!</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin: 10px 0;\">While we continue to add more value for the users at The Local Tribe, I personally look forward to your inputs as well.</p>\r\n\r\n							<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin:20px 0 10px 0 ;\">Warm greetings</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin:0px 0;\">Vineet</p>\r\n						<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin:0px 0;\">Founder @ The Local Tribe</p>\r\n						</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgb(51,51,51);text-align:center;line-height:24px;padding: 20px 0 10px 0;background: #fff;\"><font face=\"trebuchet ms, sans-serif;background:#fff;\">\r\n                                      <a href=\"http://bit.ly/TLT_Facebook\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin: 0px 0px;width:40px;white-space:nowrap;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgb(0,159,156)!important;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.thelocaltribe.com/emailer/v2/fb.png\" alt=\"Like Us\" align=\"none\" style=\"border:none;clear:both;display:inline-block;float:none;font-size:28px;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;outline:none\" class=\"CToWUd\"></a>\r\n                                      <a href=\"http://bit.ly/TLT_Twitter\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin: 0px 8px;width:40px;white-space:nowrap;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgb(0,159,156)!important;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.thelocaltribe.com/emailer/v2/tw.png\" alt=\"Tweet with Us\" align=\"none\" style=\"border:none;clear:both;display:inline-block;float:none;font-size:28px;margin:0px auto;max-width:100%;outline:none\" class=\"CToWUd\"></a>\r\n                                      \r\n                                      <a href=\"http://bit.ly/TLT_Ins